| `years_experience` | Integer | Total career years; **`0` is valid** (`BasicInfo` `ge=0`). Dashboard JS must not treat `0` as â€śemptyâ€ť (see `frontend-js-strict.mdc`, â€śRequired numeric fieldsâ€ť). |
